oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various radio spots for the Johnny Cash Show, featuring Little Jimmy Dickens (performer), Stonewall Jackson (performer), Nat Stuckey (performer), Charlie Walker (performer), Jay Lee Webb (performer), Tom T.
